{"type":"message","id":"e749c7d4","parentId":"51b22091","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:02:31.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Porque la base que tengo marcada es **torso-pierna frecuencia 2** con días de entrenamiento **miércoles, jueves, sábado y domingo**. Si hoy fue torso, mañana cae pierna para mantener el reparto y no montar dos torso seguidos sin necesidad.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0821345abba5ec180169c493b80c5081919fc1b385303dd5f4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":8290,"output":63,"cacheRead":5632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13985,"cost":{"input":0.020725,"output":0.000945,"cacheRead":0.001408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023078}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774490547415,"responseId":"resp_0821345abba5ec180169c493b6992c819193646c55d010434e"}}
